descriptionHtml:
[size=+2]Hi,i come back to modding and i make this simple mod for greater challenge and nudity lovers.I play this mod from long time ago and i decided share with others.I used armors from "Standalone Sexy Armor" mod for create this 
simple mod.This mod adds dozens of new unique sexy bosses with 
different armors,weapons,skills for each of them and their naked 
followers in many places of Skyrim.All bosses have their own skills and abilities and each of them is strong for kill.This mod was created to build a 
diversity and to bring a little challenge the game.This mod contains 
no scripts.The mod not edit leveled items and vanilla NPCs is not touched,only create new NPCs in Skyrim.
forBosses and others.[/size]

[size=+8]Recuirements:[/size]

Latest Update of Skyrim
UNP BASE Main body V1dot2 - or you can use any type of body meshes of any mod.
